archimate:Folder.name: 7.3.1.1 Phase I L1 Complete Test Stand
archimate:Folder.documentation:
First set of L1 pre-deployment testing elements.
The Phase 1 L1 complete test stand is a set of lab rersources that are used to support development, integrattion, and test of the Level 1 system. The Resources are sufficent to exercise the system at scale. The test stand supports L1 data flows up to, and including, characterization of images at NCSA. The Phase I test stand does not support difference imaging or event distribution.
